Package com.paypal.selion.pojos

A collection of POJOs (Plain old Java Objects) that are used internally.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArtifactDetails
    A Pojo class to hold the details of the artifacts that needs to be downloaded
    ArtifactDetails.URLChecksumEntity
    A simple POJO that represents the key value pair for url and checksum for a given entity.
    ProcessInfo
    A simple POJO (Plain Old Java class) that essentially captures the image name and the PID of a process.
    SeLionGridConstants
    A Class which contains String constants used throughout SeLion Grid Patterns & conventions used in naming the constants for this class

    - Anything that is a *DIR* ends with a '/'
    - Anything that is a *FILE* is a file
    - Anything that is a *URL* is relative to http://{hostname}:{port}
    - Anything that is a *RESOURCE* is a jar resource that can be loaded via the CLASSPATH
    - Anything that is a *PAGE* is a HTML page
    - Anything that is a *ARG* is a program argument
    - Any single constant may utilize more than one of these patterns/conventions
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ProcessNames
    This enum contains the list of processes that are of interest for the SeLion Grid.
    PropsKeys
    This enum is essentially a container for housing all of the keys that would be part of the download properties file.
